+/* ----------------------------------------------------------------
+ * Global MURAM data area â€” at pool + EN_INTERNAL_BUFF_POOL_SIZE
+ *
+ * Contains DSCP-to-VLAN PCP mapping (8 bytes) followed by SEC
+ * failure statistics (92 bytes).  Total: 100 bytes within a
