+ * and issue ioctls that map 1:1 to NCSW kernel functions:
+ *
+ *   FM_PCD_IOC_KG_SCHEME_SET    â†’  FM_PCD_KgSchemeSet()
+ *   FM_PCD_IOC_HASH_TABLE_SET   â†’  FM_PCD_HashTableSet()
